<details class="lab-controls" data-lab-controls>
	<summary>
		<span class="lab-controls-title"><i aria-hidden="true">✦</i> 實驗控制器</span>
		<small data-preferences-summary>讀取裝置與偏好中</small>
	</summary>

	<div class="lab-controls-panel">
		<div class="lab-controls-heading">
			<div>
				<p>Lab Environment</p>
				<h2>共用測試設定</h2>
			</div>
			<span class="lab-controls-state">F26 Shared API</span>
		</div>

		<dl class="lab-device-grid" aria-label="目前裝置資訊">
			<div><dt>Viewport</dt><dd data-viewport-output>等待 JavaScript</dd></div>
			<div><dt>DPR</dt><dd data-dpr-output>—</dd></div>
			<div><dt>Pointer</dt><dd data-pointer-output>—</dd></div>
			<div><dt>Motion</dt><dd data-motion-output>—</dd></div>
			<div><dt>效能結果</dt><dd data-performance-output>—</dd></div>
		</dl>

		<form class="lab-preferences-form" data-lab-preferences-form>
			<label>
				<span>動態偏好</span>
				<select name="motion" data-motion-control>
					<option value="full">完整動態（預設）</option>
					<option value="reduce">減少動態</option>
				</select>
				<small>所有 Lab 功能共用此設定，並跨頁保存。</small>
			</label>

			<label>
				<span>音效偏好</span>
				<select name="sound" data-sound-control>
					<option value="on">開啟（預設）</option>
					<option value="off">關閉</option>
				</select>
				<small>這一步只記住偏好，不會播放測試聲音。</small>
			</label>

			<label>
				<span>效能模式</span>
				<select name="performance" data-performance-control>
					<option value="standard">標準（預設）</option>
					<option value="economy">節能</option>
				</select>
				<small>只有明確選擇節能時才降低裝飾性效果。</small>
			</label>

			<button type="button" data-reset-preferences>重設所有偏好</button>
		</form>

		<p class="lab-controls-status" data-preferences-status aria-live="polite"></p>
		<noscript><p class="lab-controls-noscript">JavaScript 未啟用；主要內容仍可閱讀，但裝置資訊與偏好控制無法使用。</p></noscript>
	</div>
</details>

<script>
	import { initializeLabPreferences } from '../../scripts/lab/preferences';

	initializeLabPreferences();
</script>
